1. Sourcewell and Canoe are seeking proposals for Law Enforcement Equipment, construed to consist of equipment, gear, tools, and instruments (including related services), designed or used for law enforcement, corrections, security, and defense activity, criminal investigation, tactical response, and traffic enforcement, of the following types:
a. Law enforcement duty gear;
b. Traffic safety enforcement equipment, devices, and instruments;
c. Crime scene management and evidence collection equipment and supplies;
d. Tactical and Explosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD) equipment (with the exception of those items excluded in subsections 2. or 3. below); and, Rev. 3/2026 Sourcewell RFP #061626 Law Enforcement Equipment Page 5
e. Services related to the respondents offering of the solutions in subsections 1. a. - d. above, such as training, installation, testing, maintenance, warranty programs, and technical support.

Proposers may include related equipment, accessories, and services to the extent that these solutions are complementary to the equipment, products, or service(s) being proposed.

2. The focus of this solicitation is on Law Enforcement Equipment. This solicitation should NOT be construed to include: 1) firearms and ammunition; 2) conducted energy weapons or less lethal equipment; 3) uncrewed systems or 4) critical care, resuscitation, or EMS equipment.

3. This solicitation does not include those equipment, products, or services covered under categories included in contracts currently maintained by Sourcewell: with the limited exception of the solutions identified in Section 1. above:
a. Conducted Energy Weapons (RFP #092722);
b. Unmanned and Remotely Operated Vehicle Systems with Related Technology and Services; (RFP #011223);
c. Laboratory and Science Equipment, Supplies, and Related Technology and Services (RFP #020723);
d. Public Safety Video Surveillance Solutions with Related Equipment, Software and Accessories (RFP #101223);
e. Uniforms with Related Products and Services (RFP # 011124);
f. Body Armor with Related Accessories, Equipment, and Services (RFP # 091924);
g. Public Safety Communications Technology and Hardware Solutions (RFP #020625);
h. Public Safety Software (RFP #030425);
i. Laboratory and Toxicology Testing, Screening Services, and Related Solutions (RFP #101425)
j. Public Safety Training and Simulation Equipment and Technology (RFP #102325);
k. Catalog Solutions for Public Safety, Rescue, and Emergency Management (RFP #051226)
